#. HTML: <section class="sutta" id="sn2.6"><article><div class="hgroup"><p class="division">
msgctxt "sn2.6:0.1"
msgid "Saṃyutta Nikāya 2 "
msgstr "Linked Discourses 2 "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "sn2.6:0.2"
msgid "1. Paṭhamavagga "
msgstr "1. The First Chapter "

#. HTML: </p><h1>
msgctxt "sn2.6:0.3"
msgid "6. Kāmadasutta "
msgstr "6. With Kāmada "

#. HTML: </h1></div><p>
#. REF: pts2ed1.109, sc1
msgctxt "sn2.6:1.1"
msgid "Sāvatthinidānaṃ. "
msgstr "At Sāvatthī. "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "sn2.6:1.2"
msgid "Ekamantaṃ ṭhito kho kāmado devaputto bhagavantaṃ etadavoca: "
msgstr "Standing to one side, the god Kāmada said to the Buddha, "

msgctxt "sn2.6:1.3"
msgid "“dukkaraṃ, bhagavā, sudukkaraṃ, bhagavā”ti. "
msgstr "“It’s too hard, Blessed One! It’s just too hard!” "

#. HTML: </p><blockquote class="gatha"><p>
#. REF: sc2
msgctxt "sn2.6:2.1"
msgid "“Dukkaraṃ vāpi karonti, "
msgstr "“They do it even though it’s hard,” "

#. HTML: <span class="speaker">
msgctxt "sn2.6:2.2"
msgid "(kāmadāti bhagavā) "
msgstr "said the Buddha to Kāmada, "

# NOTE: See my note on AN 8.59 for silasamahita
#. HTML: </span><br>
msgctxt "sn2.6:2.3"
msgid "Sekhā sīlasamāhitā; "
msgstr "“the stable trainees with ethics, and immersion. "

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "sn2.6:2.4"
msgid "Ṭhitattā anagāriyupetassa, "
msgstr "For one who has entered the homeless life, "

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "sn2.6:2.5"
msgid "Tuṭṭhi hoti sukhāvahā”ti. "
msgstr "contentment brings happiness.” "

#. HTML: </p></blockquote><p>
#. REF: sc3
msgctxt "sn2.6:3.1"
msgid "“Dullabhā, bhagavā, yadidaṃ tuṭṭhī”ti. "
msgstr "“Such contentment, Blessed One, is hard to find.” "

#. HTML: </p><blockquote class="gatha"><p>
#. REF: sc4
msgctxt "sn2.6:4.1"
msgid "“Dullabhaṃ vāpi labhanti, "
msgstr "“They find it even though it’s hard,” "

#. HTML: <span class="speaker">
msgctxt "sn2.6:4.2"
msgid "(kāmadāti bhagavā) "
msgstr "said the Buddha to Kāmada, "

#. HTML: </span><br>
msgctxt "sn2.6:4.3"
msgid "Cittavūpasame ratā; "
msgstr "“those who love peace of mind; "

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "sn2.6:4.4"
msgid "Yesaṃ divā ca ratto ca, "
msgstr "whose minds love to meditate "

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "sn2.6:4.5"
msgid "Bhāvanāya rato mano”ti. "
msgstr "day and night.” "

#. HTML: </p></blockquote><p>
#. REF: sc5
msgctxt "sn2.6:5.1"
msgid "“Dussamādahaṃ, bhagavā, yadidaṃ cittan”ti. "
msgstr "“But it’s hard, Blessed One, to immerse this mind in samādhi.” "

#. HTML: </p><blockquote class="gatha"><p>
#. REF: sc6
msgctxt "sn2.6:6.1"
msgid "“Dussamādahaṃ vāpi samādahanti, "
msgstr "“They become immersed in samādhi even though it’s hard,” "

#. HTML: <span class="speaker">
msgctxt "sn2.6:6.2"
msgid "(kāmadāti bhagavā) "
msgstr " said the Buddha to Kāmada, "

#. HTML: </span><br>
msgctxt "sn2.6:6.3"
msgid "Indriyūpasame ratā; "
msgstr "“those who love calming the faculties. "

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "sn2.6:6.4"
msgid "Te chetvā maccuno jālaṃ, "
msgstr "Having cut through the net of Death, "

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "sn2.6:6.5"
msgid "Ariyā gacchanti kāmadā”ti. "
msgstr "the noble ones, Kāmada, go on their way.” "

#. HTML: </p></blockquote><p>
#. REF: sc7
msgctxt "sn2.6:7.1"
msgid "“Duggamo, bhagavā, visamo maggo”ti. "
msgstr "“But this path, Blessed One, is rough and hard to travel.” "

#. HTML: </p><blockquote class="gatha"><p>
#. REF: pts2ed1.110, sc8
msgctxt "sn2.6:8.1"
msgid "“Duggame visame vāpi, "
msgstr "“Though it’s rough, hard to travel, "

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "sn2.6:8.2"
msgid "Ariyā gacchanti kāmada; "
msgstr "the noble ones, Kāmada, go on their way. "

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "sn2.6:8.3"
msgid "Anariyā visame magge, "
msgstr "The ignoble fall headfirst "

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "sn2.6:8.4"
msgid "Papatanti avaṃsirā; "
msgstr "on a rough path. "

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "sn2.6:8.5"
msgid "Ariyānaṃ samo maggo, "
msgstr "But the path of the noble ones is smooth, "

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "sn2.6:8.6"
msgid "Ariyā hi visame samā”ti. "
msgstr "for the noble ones are smooth amid the rough.”"

#. HTML: </p></blockquote></article></section></body></html>
